Project Identity
----------------

TechFlag IDP Community is the open-source community edition of TechFlag's
intelligent document processing workbench. It is designed for local-first
document AI workflows, including OCR integration, document tree inspection,
evidence-grounded extraction, and reusable document application experiments.

